*.py
# Exception: tutorials code-snippet sources are tracked — they're pulled into
# the docs via pymdownx snippets (check_paths: true), so a fresh clone must
# have them or the build fails.
!tutorials-src/snippets/*.py
node_modules/
vendor/materialx/
# Regenerated by scripts/build-tutorials.mjs on every build; not the deploy artifact (that's /tutorials/).
tutorials-src/docs/assets/vendored/
# English-only search: Material's lunr language packs are pruned post-build (scripts/build-tutorials.mjs); backstop so they never get re-tracked.
tutorials/assets/javascripts/lunr/
tutorial-ideas.md